tz. Thought-Images not only reorients our understanding of the Frankfurt School of Critical Theory in important ways but also establishes significant links between these writers and contemporary French thinkers such as Jacques Derrida.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362653940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503626539423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503626539/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles